["productcatalogservice-2", "paymentservice-2", "currencyservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-1", "emailservice-2", "checkoutservice-2", "productcatalogservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-0", "adservice-1", "currencyservice-2", "cartservice-0", "frontend-1", "emailservice-0", "shippingservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["recommendationservice-2", "shippingservice-2", "paymentservice-0", "redis-cart-0", "cartservice-1", "adservice-2", "shippingservice-1", "recommendationservice-0"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault was detected from 2025-06-06T02:02:59Z to 2025-06-06T02:15:59Z. Please analyze its root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-06 02:02:59+00:00 to 2025-06-06 02:15:59+00:00"}, "metric_data_collected": true, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["checkoutservice-1", "emailservice-1", "shippingservice-1", "recommendationservice-1", "productcatalogservice-0", "productcatalogservice-1", "shippingservice-0", "recommendationservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["recommendationservice-0", "frontend-0", "paymentservice-1", "cartservice-2", "adservice-0", "productcatalogservice-2", "recommendationservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["frontend-2", "checkoutservice-0", "currencyservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["productcatalogservice-2", "paymentservice-2", "currencyservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-1", "emailservice-2", "checkoutservice-2", "productcatalogservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-0", "adservice-1", "currencyservice-2", "cartservice-0", "frontend-1", "emailservice-0", "shippingservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["recommendationservice-2", "shippingservice-2", "paymentservice-0", "redis-cart-0", "cartservice-1", "adservice-2", "shippingservice-1", "recommendationservice-0"]}, "available_metric_names": ["client_error_ratio", "error_ratio", "pod_cpu_usage", "rrt", "rrt_max", "server_error_ratio"], "metric_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"server_error_ratio\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant increase in error_ratio and client_error_ratio, indicating a possible failure or issue in this specific pod.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio increased from 0.0 to 40.0; client_error_ratio increased from 0.0 to 40.0.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"High increase in rrt and rrt_max, suggesting performance degradation affecting response times.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt increased from 12214.98 to 194901.15; rrt_max from 261778.0 to 60002302.04.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"Extreme increase in rrt, pointing to major latency issues.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt increased from 7019.66 to 1015066.59.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "log_analysis_findings": "根据日志分析显示，在 UUID 为 d3bd27f3-90 的异常期间，以下为提取和分析的结果：\n\n### 检测到的日志关键词\n- transport\n- Error while dialing\n- i/o timeout\n- context canceled\n- connection error\n- timed out waiting for server handshake\n\n### 分析与假设\n从提供的日志信息来看，有几个显著的故障模式被识别出：\n\n1. **连接故障和 I/O 超时**:\n   - **日志关键字**: `\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.27.213:50051: i/o timeout\"`\n   - **发生次数**: 多次（occurrence count 非常高）\n   - **涉及服务**: `frontend`\n   - **推测原因**: 在和 `shipping service` 的 RPC 通信中产生超时。这可能暗示网络不稳定或目标服务无响应。\n\n2. **上下文取消**:\n   - **日志关键字**: `\"context canceled\"`\n   - **发生次数**: 14 次\n   - **涉及服务**: `frontend`\n   - **推测原因**: 请求被取消，这类型的错误通常与服务间的通信失败有关，常见因请求超时或重试策略生效而终止待处理请求。\n\n### 具体假设\n- **连接超时故障**: 网络问题或服务未能接收请求（服务不可用或高负载）。\n  - **evidence**: 日志多次报告 `i/o timeout`，请求未能完成，并伴随着“shipping quote failure”错误描述。\n\n- **DNS 可能故障**: 由于大量的 `transport` 和 `Error while dialing` 及其 `i/o timeout`，可能存在 DNS 解析故障导致的连接问题。\n\n### JSON 格式输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"transport\", \"Error while dialing\", \"i/o timeout\", \"context canceled\", \"connection error\", \"timed out waiting for server handshake\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"大量连接超时，可能由网络问题或服务无响应引起，涉及到 transport 错误和 I/O 超时。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.27.213:50051: i/o timeout\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"上下文取消表明正在和 shipping service 通信的过程中请求被终止，可能因回应超时或重试策略。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n请据此考虑网络调试，确认 `shipping service` 服务的可用性及相关网络环境是否正常。", "trace_analysis_findings": "根据UUID `d3bd27f3-90` 的追踪信息分析，存在以下显著异常调用链和状态组合：\n\n### 异常调用链和延迟分析\n- **Checkout Service → Shipping Service**\n  - 操作: `hipstershop.ShippingService/GetQuote`\n  - 正常平均耗时: 9347ms, 异常时段平均耗时: 28310198ms\n  - 异常次数: 25\n  - 延迟增加: \\(\\frac{28310198}{9347} \\approx 3027.4\\)倍\n\n- **Frontend → Checkout Service**\n  - 操作: `hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder`\n  - 正常平均耗时: 145475ms, 异常时段平均耗时: 28988551ms\n  - 异常次数: 22\n  - 延迟增加: \\(\\frac{28988551}{145475} \\approx 199.2\\)倍\n\n### 状态码组合及错误传播路径\n- **Checkout Service 调用 Shipping Service**\n  - 错误: 超时和连接失败（\"connection error: desc = \\\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.27.213:50051: i/o timeout\\\"\"）\n  - 状态码 14（连接错误）、状态码 13（Unavailable，连接超时）\n  - 此错误从 CheckoutService 向下传播到 Frontend，导致 Frontend 响应 500 错误码。\n\n### 结论\n根本原因似乎来源于 Checkout Service 和 Shipping Service 之间的连接问题，主要是由于连接超时导致的。Frontend 的问题是对这一下游服务故障的响应，而非自身引发的问题。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Shipping Service\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Connection errors and timeouts leading to sigificant latency increase in the call chain from CheckoutService to ShippingService.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Checkout Service\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Propagation of the connection error to Frontend with status code 500.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n这个信息可用于进一步的故障排查，重点检查 Shipping Service 是否存在网络配置或资源问题导致的连接故障。"}
